title: IAA Tonight | Spida Mitchell Gets Traded to the Cavaliers AND Kansas City Chiefs Season Preview
description: Donovan Mitchell is finally traded out of Utah and is headed to Cleveland to play for the up and coming Cavaliers, but is this enough to get Cleveland over the hump and into the playoffs? Antoine Walker and Ashley Nicole Moss get into a passionate debate on whether this was a good move for Cleveland. We continue our Countdown to Kickoff with the Kansas City Chiefs. Find out where Brandon Marshall ranks them in the AFC West.
author: smanderville@houseofathlete.com (Brandon Marshall, Ashley Nicole Moss, Antoine Walker)
